<section class="section hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content reveal">
      <h1>{gettext("The language OS for your organization")}</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        {gettext(
          "Glossia captures your linguistic preferences in one place so linguists and teams can shape how your organization speaks across every language and surface."
        )}
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="button primary" href={~p"/interest"}>{gettext("Get started")}</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href={~p"/docs"}>{gettext("Check out the docs")}</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-logos">
        <span class="hero-logos-label">{gettext("From builders who worked at")}</span>
        <div class="hero-logos-row">
          <a href="https://soundcloud.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src={~p"/assets/logos/soundcloud.svg"} alt="SoundCloud" height="14" />
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.shopify.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src={~p"/assets/logos/shopify.svg"} alt="Shopify" height="26" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="geo-accent" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 320 320" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect
          x="40"
          y="40"
          width="120"
          height="120"
          rx="8"
          stroke="#7c3aed"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          opacity="0.2"
        />
        <rect
          x="100"
          y="100"
          width="120"
          height="120"
          rx="8"
          stroke="#f59e0b"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          opacity="0.15"
        />
        <rect
          x="160"
          y="60"
          width="100"
          height="100"
          rx="8"
          stroke="#059669"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          opacity="0.12"
        />
        <circle cx="80" cy="260" r="30" stroke="#7c3aed" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.1" />
        <circle cx="260" cy="200" r="20" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.1" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section community-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="community-banner-content reveal">
      <div class="community-banner-text">
        <h2>{gettext("Join the community")}</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          {gettext(
            "Chat with the team, share feedback, and connect with other builders using Glossia."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        class="button primary community-discord-button"
        href="https://discord.gg/7FRHkwvs"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        <svg
          width="20"
          height="16"
          viewBox="0 0 71 55"
          fill="currentColor"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path d="M60.1 4.9A58.5 58.5 0 0 0 45.4.2a.2.2 0 0 0-.2.1 40.8 40.8 0 0 0-1.8 3.7 54 54 0 0 0-16.2 0A37.4 37.4 0 0 0 25.4.3a.2.2 0 0 0-.2-.1A58.4 58.4 0 0 0 10.5 5a.2.2 0 0 0-.1 0A59.7 59.7 0 0 0 .3 45.3a.3.3 0 0 0 0 .2 58.9 58.9 0 0 0 17.7 9a.2.2 0 0 0 .3-.1 42.1 42.1 0 0 0 3.6-5.9.2.2 0 0 0-.1-.3 38.8 38.8 0 0 1-5.5-2.6.2.2 0 0 1 0-.4l1.1-.9a.2.2 0 0 1 .2 0 42 42 0 0 0 35.8 0 .2.2 0 0 1 .2 0l1.1.9a.2.2 0 0 1 0 .3 36.4 36.4 0 0 1-5.5 2.7.2.2 0 0 0-.1.3 47.2 47.2 0 0 0 3.6 5.9.2.2 0 0 0 .3.1 58.7 58.7 0 0 0 17.7-9 .2.2 0 0 0 .1-.2c1.4-14.8-.3-29.5-10-45.2a.2.2 0 0 0-.1-.1ZM23.7 37.1c-3.9 0-7.1-3.6-7.1-8s3.1-8 7.1-8 7.2 3.6 7.1 8-3.1 8-7.1 8Zm26.2 0c-3.9 0-7.1-3.6-7.1-8s3.1-8 7.1-8 7.2 3.6 7.1 8-3.1 8-7.1 8Z" />
        </svg>
        {gettext("Join our Discord")}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="why" class="section section-accent">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="reveal">{gettext("Why a language OS")}</h2>
    <p class="muted lead reveal">
      {gettext(
        "Your organization already has systems for code, design, and data. Language deserves the same level of care."
      )}
    </p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M12 7v14m-9-3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <strong>{gettext("One source of truth for how you speak")}</strong>
        <p>
          {gettext(
            "All of your linguistic preferences live in one place. Every team draws from the same foundation, so your organization sounds consistent whether it is a product screen, a marketing campaign, or a support reply."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20M2 12h20" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <strong>{gettext("Speak new languages, reach new markets")}</strong>
        <p>
          {gettext(
            "The same linguistic foundation that keeps your content consistent also powers expansion into new languages. Linguists refine the voice once, and every market benefits from that work immediately."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M12 22v-5m3-9V2m2 6a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a4 4 0 0 1-4 4h-4a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V9a1 1 0 0 1 1-1zM9 8V2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <strong>{gettext("Bring context to the tools you already use")}</strong>
        <p>
          {gettext("Glossia integrates with your existing workflows through")}
          <a href={~p"/docs/reference/api"}>{gettext("APIs")}</a>
          {gettext("and open standards like")}
          <a href="https://modelcontextprotocol.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MCP</a>. {gettext(
            "Your writing tools, content platforms, and AI assistants can all tap into your organization's linguistic knowledge without switching systems."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="capabilities" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="reveal">{gettext("Built on the foundation, ready for your use cases")}</h2>
    <p class="muted lead reveal">
      {gettext(
        "We build solutions on top of the language OS, and you can build your own. The same foundation powers everything."
      )}
    </p>
    <div class="tools-grid tools-grid-2col">
      <div class="card tool-card reveal" data-interactive>
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M12 8V4H8" /><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2" /><path d="M2 14h2m16 0h2m-7-1v2m-6-2v2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>{gettext("Agentic localization and content revisiting")}</h3>
        <p>
          {gettext(
            "AI agents translate, adapt, and refine your content, guided by your linguistic preferences. When context changes, the system knows what is affected and revisits it automatically."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card tool-card reveal" data-interactive>
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M15 6a9 9 0 0 0-9 9V3" /><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3" /><circle
              cx="6"
              cy="18"
              r="3"
            />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>{gettext("Context graph")}</h3>
        <p>
          {gettext(
            "A queryable map that connects your voices, glossaries, audiences, and rules. Agents and integrations query it at runtime, so every decision a linguist makes flows through to every piece of content it touches."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card tool-card reveal" data-interactive>
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M10 22V7a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H2" /><rect
              width="8"
              height="8"
              x="14"
              y="2"
              rx="1"
            />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>{gettext("Open integrations")}</h3>
        <p>
          {gettext("Build your own solutions on top of the foundation through")}
          <a href={~p"/docs/reference/api"}>{gettext("REST APIs")}</a>
          {gettext("and")}
          <a href="https://modelcontextprotocol.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MCP</a>. {gettext(
            "Connect your writing platforms, content systems, and AI assistants to your organization's linguistic knowledge."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card tool-card reveal" data-interactive>
        <div class="step-number">
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" /><circle
              cx="9"
              cy="7"
              r="4"
            />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>{gettext("Linguist-centered collaboration")}</h3>
        <p>
          {gettext(
            "Linguists review, refine, and approve content directly. They are not at the end of a chain but at the center, shaping how your organization speaks before anything ships."
          )}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="platform" class="section section-accent">
